Class Server

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • mayflower.net.Server
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public abstract class Server
extends java.lang.Thread
    The parent class for Server programs.

    Listens for connections from and manages Client programs.
